g.ns11:text: \\begin{align*}\n&f_t = \\sigma (W_f \\cdot [h_{t-1}, x_t] + b_f) \\\\\n&i_t = \\sigma (W_i \\cdot [h_{t-1}, x_t] + b_i) \\\\\n&\\tilde{C_t} = \\text{tanh} (W_C \\cdot [h_{t-1}, x_t] + b_C) \\\\\n&C_t = f_t * C_{t-1} = i_t * \\tilde{C_t} \\\\\n&o_t = \\sigma (W-o [h_{t-1}, x_t] + b_o) \\\\\n&h_t = o_t * \\text{tanh} (C_t)\n\\end{align*}
